data.description: Location Location! See this solid built 1940's beachside home that is conveniently located in Daytona Beach. Charming 3/2 plan has tile floors throughout, updated electric and 2017 roof.  Kitchen has been updated with ample solid wood cabinets, range hood, and granite countertops. Like to cook with gas? No problem this neighborhood has natural gas service and the range & gas tankless water heater are already in place.  The larger lot has a nice back private back yard with a 21'x18'  paver patio area.  Ideal for family cookouts and room for a future pool. There is also a 2 car garage.  Walk or bike to the public beach access only 2 1/2 short blocks at the end of the street. Daytona Playhouse is just 3 blocks away. Like to fish the river? Colin Park is 4 blocks. Enjoy the ocean breeze while living in this quiet residential area.  The Ocean Center is 1 mile away and the Hard Rock Hotel is a 5 min walk.
